==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unparalleled
<hw>Un*par"al*leled</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having no
parallel, or equal; unequaled; unmatched.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>unparalleled</qex> perseverance of the armies of the
United States, under every suffering and discouragement, was little
short of a miracle.</q> <rj><qau>Washington.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unparched</ent>⟦br⟧
